走吧！
Let's go!

1283
01:54:12,557 --> 01:54:13,546
准备好了
She's armed.

1284
01:54:14,025 --> 01:54:16,084
希望你不在那里
You better not be up there.

1285
01:54:16,595 --> 01:54:18,426
走吧！快点！
Let's go! Come on!

1286
