我们只剩一颗炮弹，对吧？
We only have one round left, right?

1288
01:54:38,216 --> 01:54:39,046
对
Yeah.

1289
01:54:50,228 --> 01:54:52,492
和您服役是我的荣幸，舰长
It was an honor serving with you, Captain.

1290
01:54:55,300 --> 01:54:56,824
荣幸的是我
The honor was mine.

1291
01:55:01,906 --> 01:55:03,601
