长官
Sir...

1344
01:59:54,399 --> 01:59:56,731
我拯救了世界耶
I saved the world.

1345
01:59:57,402 --> 02:00:01,065
拯救世界和我女儿是两回事
Saving the world is one thing, Hopper. My daughter is quite another.

1346
02:00:02,206 --> 02:00:05,642
但是  - 不准就是不准
